text: Fatima-Zahra Hafdi (born 25 August 1988), known by her stage name La Zarra, is a Canadian-Moroccan singer who lives in France. In 2021, she became popular with the single "Tu t'en iras", which was was certified platinum by the SNEP. La Zarra represented France in the 2023 Eurovision Contest with the song "Ã‰videmment". She finished in 16th place out of 26 finalists.
